title: First Spaceship on Venus, The (Schweigende Stern, Der)

sources.title: First Spaceship on Venus, The (Schweigende Stern, Der)
sources.description: Taken from IMDB : (U.S. Version) A mysterious magnetic spool found during a construction project is discovered to have originated from Venus. A rocket expedition to Venus is launched to discover the origin of the spool and the race that created it.
